Telkom has launched itsÂ Big Deal for September 2019. The deal allows users to sign up for a FreeMe 20GB contract at a discounted rate of R499 per month on a 24-month contract. This includes 20GB of mobile data, as well as 62GB of additional specific-use data for certain applications, 3,000 on-net minutes, and 1,500 any-net minutes. Included in this deal is: The September Big Deal is a SIM-only deal, meaning that you will need to use the SIM in your smart device, or purchase your own router. Music and video streaming data can only be used on platforms compatible with the Telkom LIT offering, including Netflix, Showmax, and YouTube. This deal is available until 30 September 2019. 